- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses machine learning algorithms for classification and prediction.
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a possible category as the paper deals with analyzing call detail records in cellular networks.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a possible category as the paper deals with predicting traffic load using historical data.
